{"tid":1813483,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★美聯主席：社會事件緩和，樓市「小陽春」已開始！","createTime":"2020-01-06T10:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T09:02:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"58bf754e947ef6311402e1200b8d556043281152","tid":1813483,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:05:07.000Z","msg":"美聯集團（1200）主席黃建業估計，今年樓價會呈「U型」，先跌後升最多5%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在中美兩國簽署貿易協議，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">及社會事件緩和下</span></strong>，今年上半年跌幅收窄；去年10月政府放寬按保限制，加上新盤熱銷帶動，已令樓市提早進入「小陽春」，惟「陽春早至，來去匆匆」，預料會於農曆新年後完結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/418253/%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E9%BB%83%E5%BB%BA%E6%A5%AD-%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82-%E5%B0%8F%E9%99%BD%E6%98%A5-%E5%B7%B2%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B-%E6%96%99%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E5%83%85%E5%8D%875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F418253%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2581%25AF%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%2599%25BD%25E6%2598%25A5-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A7%258B-%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2583%2585%25E5%258D%25875&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=0cc23d2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/418253/%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E9%BB%83%E5%BB%BA%E6%A5%AD-%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82-%E5%B0%8F%E9%99%BD%E6%98%A5-%E5%B7%B2%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B-%E6%96%99%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E5%83%85%E5%8D%875</a>"},{"pid":"8dee20d0b918a8c5a0ecc56c514451232f26012c","tid":1813483,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:05:40.000Z","msg":"運動已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de60001698b264a91bb0c4134b814ab62e1e5437","tid":1813483,"uid":19454,"like":0,"disli